text: Oschiri (Óschiri, Óscari) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Sassari in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 3,293 people lived there. Its area is 215.61 km². It is 202 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Sassari
title: Oschiri
